  CONFIG
  IS_PAUSED
  COMP
  S

PURE format_title

IO set_title
  IS_PLAYING
  S

IO display_rows
  COMP
  S

IO query_streams
  Icecast
  Radio

PURE add_rows_padding
PURE icecast_list
PURE radio_list
PURE format_stream_list


